  • Uses of TokenCodes in remodel.io

    Classes in remodel.io that implement TokenCodes 
    Modifier and Type Class Description
    class  ConceptCompiler
    ConceptCompiler is a cross-compiler that translates a ReMoDeL concept into a Java source file.
    class  ExpressionCompiler
    ExpressionCompiler is an abstract cross-compiler that translates ReMoDeL expressions into equivalent Java expressions.
    class  ExpressionReader
    ExpressionReader is the abstract ancestor of parsers which analyse code expressions.
    class  ExpressionWriter
    ExpressionWriter is the abstract ancestor of pretty-printers that format code expressions.
    class  MetamodelReader
    MetamodelReader is a parser for ReMoDeL metamodels.
    class  MetamodelWriter
    MetamodelWriter is a pretty-printer for ReMoDeL metamodels.
    class  ModelReader
    ModelReader is a parser for ReMoDeL models.
    class  ModelScanner
    ModelScanner is a tokenizer to support parsing ReMoDeL models, metamodels and transformations.
    class  SymbolCompiler
    SymbolCompiler is an abstract compiler for translating names and types.
    class  TransformCompiler
    TransformCompiler is a cross-compiler that translates a ReMoDeL transformation into a Java source file.
    class  TransformReader
    TransformReader is a parser for ReMoDeL transformations.
    class  TransformWriter
    TransformWriter is a pretty-printer for ReMoDeL transformations.
